I understand.

79
00:05:03,140 --> 00:05:04,940
You have one on your neck as well.

80
00:05:05,540 --> 00:05:06,060
Don't move.

81
00:05:19,380 --> 00:05:19,940
Done.

82
00:05:21,780 --> 00:05:23,220
This is my mother's secret formula.

83
00:05:23,460 --> 00:05:24,460
Isn't it effective?

84
00:05:27,460 --> 00:05:28,300
I don't think

85
00:05:28,380 --> 00:05:29,620
I've ever seen you before.

86
00:05:29,940 --> 00:05:31,100
Which courtyard are you from?

87
00:05:31,500 --> 00:05:32,300
Madam Mu,

88
00:05:32,310 --> 00:05:33,900
