99
00:06:12,100 --> 00:06:13,140
You're a maid.

100
00:06:13,380 --> 00:06:14,860
Do I need a reason to hit you?

101
00:06:20,820 --> 00:06:21,700
How dare you hit me?

102
00:06:22,140 --> 00:06:22,780
Madam Chunxiao,

103
00:06:22,900 --> 00:06:23,980
I must return this slap.

104
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:26,210
My mother said I've had demonic energy
since I was little.

105
00:06:26,220 --> 00:06:27,900
If someone hits me,
I must hit them back.

106
00:06:28,080 --> 00:06:30,340
Otherwise, the one who hit me
will lose their blessings.

107
00:06:30,660 --> 00:06:31,660
You dare mock me?

108
00:06:31,660 --> 00:06:32,820
I haven't finished.

109
00:06:33,020 --> 00:06:33,620
Madam Chunxiao.

110
00:06:34,220 --> 00:06:35,380
