131
00:07:35,020 --> 00:07:36,100
With just a blind man

132
00:07:36,500 --> 00:07:37,540
and a maid?

133
00:07:49,220 --> 00:07:50,740
I'll be your eyes,

134
00:07:51,420 --> 00:07:52,700
so you won't be blind.

135
00:07:54,060 --> 00:07:55,500
You'll be my backbone,

136
00:07:56,340 --> 00:07:57,540
so I'll no longer be a maid.

137
00:07:59,220 --> 00:08:00,060
(Even so,)

138
00:08:01,260 --> 00:08:03,780
(we're just two ants
clinging to each other for warmth.)

139
00:08:05,100 --> 00:08:05,940
(Without strength,)

140
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:08,380
(how can we bring down a mountain?)

141
00:08:11,620 --> 00:08:12,890
(Since we don't have strength,)

142
00:08:13,860 --> 00:08:15,580
(we must find a way)

143
00:08:15,620 --> 00:08:16,500
(to obtain it.)

144
00:08:18,210 --> 00:08:19,180
(What do you plan to do?)

145
00:08:26,180 --> 00:08:26,740
Young Master,

146
00:08:27,260 --> 00:08:28,420
to bring down Zhang Wencai,

147
00:08:29,100 --> 00:08:29,860
what we need

148
00:08:30,300 --> 00:08:31,740
is a higher patron.

149
00:08:33,100 --> 00:08:34,300
