a perfume for me.

158
00:08:58,420 --> 00:08:58,860
Today,

159
00:08:59,180 --> 00:09:00,220
I've come to collect it.

160
00:09:01,060 --> 00:09:01,660
Of course.

161
00:09:01,800 --> 00:09:02,860
Governor, please come in.

162
